    "description": "ON THE PAGE, Inc. engages in the bridal business in Japan and internationally. The company offers wedding-related services, including venue guidance, wedding day planning, food and gift selection, and day management. It also operates in-house produced facilities under the MONOLITH, AMANDAN, RENOVATION, and KIRANAH RESORT brand names; dress shops that sells and rents wedding dresses, tuxedos, and japanese attire under the NOVARESE and ecruspose brands; restaurants that provides food and drinks for weddings and banquets, as well as planning and advice for afterparties and banquet; and WEDO, a system that supports wedding preparations. In addition, the company offers bridal business consulting and m&a, utilization of unclosed/unused facilities, market and BPR consulting, and item partnerships, as well as education, training, and recruitment consulting services for venue managers, financial institutions, and recruitment and training managers. Further, it involved in photography and video business; flower arrangement business; party dress rental business under the ANDYOU DRESSING ROOM name; advertising agency business; overseas wedding business; and provision of legal consultation services for the bridal industry, as well as operates recruitment agency. The company was formerly known as Novarese, Inc. and changed its name to ON THE PAGE, Inc. in April 2026. ON THE PAGE, Inc. was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Chuo, Japan."
